<paragraph id="166F2883431B9C14C85D3705B83A12AB" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
New Caledonia. Nord: 
<normalizedToken id="FA34C65C9899919A63A14922CD9A5404" originalValue="Tiébaghi">Tiebaghi</normalizedToken>
Massif, ca. 12 air-km northwest of Koumac, 8 Nov 1980 (fl, fr), 
<emphasis id="08DCD19E3FD597A67C061442E1FD10CA" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">G. McPherson 3303</emphasis>
